OL,3,CCCTV captures moment teens
OL,4,C'congratulate' each other after
OL,5,Ckilling Kayden Moy
OL,7,FWatch the moment three teenage boys
OL,8,F'celebrate' after murdering 16-year-
OL,9,Fold Kayden Moy on a beach in Ayreshire.
OL,11,FThree teenagers who were captured on
OL,12,FCCTV congratulating each other after
OL,13,Fmurdering a 16-year-old boy on a
OL,14,Fbeach, have been sentenced.
OL,16,FJay Stewart, 19; Cole Turley, 18; and
OL,17,Fa 15-year-old boy who cannot be named
OL,18,Ffor legal reasons, acted together to
OL,19,Fcarry out the attack on Kayden Moy at
OL,20,FIrvine beach, Ayrshire on May 17 2025.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
