PN,31702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1784701089
OL,3,CCCTV captures moment teens
OL,4,C'congratulate' each other after
OL,5,Ckilling Kayden Moy
OL,7,FCCTV footage released by police
OL,8,Fcaptured the moment Kayden's killers
OL,9,Fran away from the scene of the crime,
OL,10,Fappearing to congratulate each other.
OL,12,FOne clip shows the trio running back
OL,13,Fthrough the town after the attack,
OL,14,Fwith Stewart and Turley apparently
OL,15,Fshaking hands as they did so.
OL,17,FOn Tuesday, the three teenagers were
OL,18,Fsentenced at the High Court in Glasgow.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
