PN,31703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1784701089
OL,3,CCCTV captures moment teens
OL,4,C'congratulate' each other after
OL,5,Ckilling Kayden Moy
OL,7,FTurley admitted the killing, while
OL,8,FStewart and the 15-year-old were found
OL,9,Fguilty of murder last month.
OL,11,FIn his sentencing remarks, Judge Lord
OL,12,FScott said they had appeared to
OL,13,F"celebrate" the crime.
OL,15,FOne clip shows the three teenagers in
OL,16,Fsand dunes at Irvine beach after the
OL,17,Fattack.
