OL,3,CCCTV captures moment teens
OL,4,C'congratulate' each other after
OL,5,Ckilling Kayden Moy
OL,7,FStewart can be seen bare-chested and
OL,8,Fholding a cosh ` a small, handheld,
OL,9,Fblunt weapon. He appears to shout at
OL,10,Fcrowds on the dunes as Turley runs to
OL,11,Fhim.
OL,13,FIn another clip, the trio can be seen
OL,14,Fin an East Kilbride stairwell
OL,15,Ffollowing the attack.
