OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1784701089
OL,3,CCCTV captures moment teens
OL,4,C'congratulate' each other after
OL,5,Ckilling Kayden Moy
OL,7,FA still image released by the Crown
OL,8,FOffice and Procurator Fiscal Service
OL,9,F(COPFS) shows the accused walking away
OL,10,Ffrom the crime scene after the attack
OL,11,Fthat killed Kayden.
OL,13,FThe footage was released after the
OL,14,Fthree teenagers were sentenced on
OL,15,FTuesday.
OL,17,FThe judge sentenced both Stewart and
OL,18,FTurley to a minimum of 16 years in
OL,19,Fdetention, and the 15-year-old to a
OL,20,Fminimum of 14 years.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
