OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1784701089
OL,3,CCCTV captures moment teens
OL,4,C'congratulate' each other after
OL,5,Ckilling Kayden Moy
OL,7,FSpeaking outside court after the
OL,8,Fhearing, Kayden's father Paul Moy said
OL,9,Fhis son had had "his whole life ahead
OL,10,Fof him".
OL,12,F"Every birthday, every family
OL,13,Fgathering, every milestone from now on
OL,14,Fwill be a reminder that he should be
OL,15,Fhere with us," he said.
